    <section class="trips-section">
      <h2>Adventure Trips</h2>
      <p>Discover our range of exciting rafting trips, each designed to provide a unique experience on the water. Below are the details for each adventure, including trip descriptions and the equipment provided.</p>
      
      <div class="trip-details">
        <h3>Los Dientes del Diablo</h3>
        <img src="images/los-dientes-del-diablo.jpg" alt="Los Dientes del Diablo">
        <p>Experience the thrill of "Los Dientes del Diablo," our most challenging trip featuring intense rapids and breathtaking scenery. This adventure is perfect for experienced rafters seeking an adrenaline rush.</p>
        <h4>Included Equipment:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>High-performance raft</li>
          <li>Safety helmet</li>
          <li>Life jacket</li>
          <li>Oars</li>
          <li>Wet suit</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="trip-details">
        <h3>Big Mallard</h3>
        <img src="images/big-mallard.jpg" alt="Big Mallard">
        <p>Our "Big Mallard" trip offers a thrilling experience with moderate rapids suitable for both beginners and seasoned rafters. Enjoy a scenic journey through lush landscapes and exciting water challenges.</p>
        <h4>Included Equipment:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Standard raft</li>
          <li>Safety helmet</li>
          <li>Life jacket</li>
          <li>Oars</li>
          <li>Wet suit</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="trip-details">
        <h3>Half Day Adventure</h3>
        <img src="images/half-day-adventure.jpg" alt="Half Day Adventure">
        <p>The "Half Day Adventure" is a shorter trip designed for those looking for a quick but exhilarating experience on the water. Perfect for families and first-time rafters.</p>
        <h4>Included Equipment:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>Standard raft</li>
          <li>Safety helmet</li>
          <li>Life jacket</li>
          <li>Oars</li>
          <li>Wet suit</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="trip-details">
        <h3>Full Day Adventure</h3>
        <img src="images/full-day-adventure.jpg" alt="Full Day Adventure">
        <p>Join us for a full day of excitement on the "Full Day Adventure." This trip includes extended rafting time, allowing you to experience a variety of rapids and scenic spots throughout the day.</p>
        <h4>Included Equipment:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>High-performance raft</li>
          <li>Safety helmet</li>
          <li>Life jacket</li>
          <li>Oars</li>
          <li>Wet suit</li>
          <li>Waterproof gear bag</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="trip-details">
        <h3>Extreme Adventure</h3>
        <img src="images/extreme-adventure.jpg" alt="Extreme Adventure">
        <p>The "Extreme Adventure" is designed for thrill-seekers looking for the most challenging rapids and wildest ride. This trip is not for the faint-hearted but offers an unparalleled adrenaline rush.</p>
        <h4>Included Equipment:</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>High-performance raft</li>
          <li>Safety helmet</li>
          <li>Life jacket</li>
          <li>Oars</li>
          <li>Wet suit</li>
          <li>Protective gloves</li>
        </ul>
